## 10. MVP Success Criteria

The system should allow any admin, mentor, or director to answer, within 10 seconds:

- Has a student paid fees?
- Which batch is a student in?
- What subjects is a student taking?
- Which chapter is a batch covering?
- Which room is allocated?
- Which exams are upcoming?
- Which students have low attendance?
- Which fees are pending?
- Which batches have not had a test this month?

If all these questions can be answered instantly, Shiksharthi OS is successful.

